headline: Trane Technologies Delivers Leading Business and Sustainability Performance by Reducing Customers' Energy Use and Carbon Emissions
summary: Trane Technologies (NYSE: TT), a global climate innovator, is continuing to set the pace for decarbonizing buildings, industry and the cold chain by reducing energy use and carbon emissions for customers and in its own operations – while consistently delivering leading business and sustainability performance.
